content: Standing Up For Ukraine. Buy an NFT and support the people of Ukraine. We donate all the proceeds to Red Cross that provides humanitarian help to the people of Ukraine. Ukraine and its people need all the support right now. So, we're using this campaign to fully support the fight for freedom in Ukraine. Buy the NFT and support the people of Ukraine. Show your support by sharing it, use it as your avatar, and invite your friends to do the same. That's our way of saying: "Stay strong! The whole world stands with you. Slava Ukraini!" Team Single.Earth
